text: Habenaria mossii is a species of plant in the Orchidaceae family. It is naturally found in South Africa. Its natural habitat is mild grassland. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==Source== * Pfab, M.F. & Victor, J. 2003. Habenaria mossii. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007. Category:Orchids
title: Habenaria mossii
